name: M. Jahangir Alam, FCMA
about: As said by Robert Louis Stevenson, “Don’t judge each day by the harvest you reap, but by the seeds you plant,” I believe in sowing the seeds of change for the future generation. To build a flourishing and sustainable future that promotes a world of equity and opportunity.
